data.description:
**Charming Ranch Home - A Rare Gem in the Heart of Town**

Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this delightful one-level ranch home, nestled on a peaceful .29 acre lot in Historic Rogersville. This never-before-sold property offers a unique opportunity for homebuyers seeking a blend of in-town living with the tranquility of a spacious, level yard.

Nice updates to this move in ready, 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with a large eat- in kitchen and carport make this one you need to see to fully appreciate.  This property offers mature trees, open level backyard space for gardening or playing, a well loved home, neutral paint and flooring, all while being in town and convenient to shopping and dining. The utility room is located by the side door and covered by the carport, washer and dryer convey. 

This house is light, bright and open, ready for you to make it your home.  Call your Realtor today to make an appointment to see this beautiful property.
